<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url(<%= image_path('pitch.jpg') %>);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="banner-info">
      <h1>OptiRecruit</h1>
      <p>Discover the world's best talent.</p>
      <% if false %>
        <%= link_to players_path, class: 'btn btn-primary mt-3' do %>
          Search <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
      <div class="mt-3">
        <%= render 'shared/search_bar' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col col-sm-10 col-md-6">
      <h3>The Project</h3>
      <p class="mb-3">Outfield players dataset - Total number of players : 22102. </p>
      <p class="mb-3">Goal-keepers dataset - Total number of players : 2781</p>
      <p class="mb-3">❗ 💡 Note: The recommendation matrix is a measure of cosine similarity that looks at the angle between two vectors and allow to capture "style".</p>
      <div class="col-6 mb-3">
        <%= image_tag "matrix.png", class: "w-100" %>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-3">💶 The predicted transfer values were predicted using a standard linear regressions model.</p>
      <p class="mb-3">🌏 Our presentation slides can be found <%= link_to 'here.', 'https://prezi.com/view/bXbjIZ2h9ychguX1mqIB' %></p>
      <p class="mb-3">💻 The code for this project is available <%= link_to 'here.', 'https://github.com/riadh-anis/opti_recruit' %></p>
      <p class="mb-3">💻 The code for the front-end is available <%= link_to 'here.', 'https://github.com/dmbf29/opti_recruit_fe' %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
